  "keyFeatures": [
    "Install, uninstall, and reinstall the ConnectWise Automate (LabTech) agent via MSI or installer token",
    "Start, stop, and restart LTService and LTSvcMon Windows services",
    "Read and expose agent registry configuration as PowerShell objects",
    "Configure and persist proxy settings for all module communications",
    "Encode and decode LabTech security strings (Base64 with key)",
    "Backup and restore agent service configuration",
    "Test connectivity to LabTech server ports",
    "Control Add/Remove Programs visibility and display name",
    "Compatible with PowerShell v2+ and both 32-bit and 64-bit environments",
    "Supports -WhatIf and -Confirm for all destructive operations"
  ],
